OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FThe boy also admitted causing a child
OL,8,Fover 13 to engage in sexual activity
OL,9,Fwithout consent. He had previously
OL,10,Fpleaded guilty to one count of
OL,11,Fperverting the course of justice,
OL,12,Fthree counts of making indecent
OL,13,Fphotographs of a child and one count
OL,14,Fof possession of extreme pornography.
