OL,3,CSheffield boy first youngster to be
OL,4,Cconvicted for encouraging self-harm
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Police pursued a
OL,8,Fcharge under Section 184 of the Online
OL,9,FSafety Act 2023. The conviction is the
OL,10,Fforce's first charge and conviction
OL,11,Ffor this offence, and the first
OL,12,Fconviction in the country of a
OL,13,Fjuvenile offender.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Scott
OL,16,FHarrison said: "Although this is a
OL,17,Fmilestone for our force in terms of
OL,18,Fprotecting a vulnerable victim through
OL,19,Fthe use of this new legislation,
OL,20,Fcircumstances surrounding the case are
OL,21,Fextremely distressing and concerning."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
