OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FHe added, "We live in a digital world
OL,8,Fwhere technology has become a key part
OL,9,Fof all our lives. The introduction of
OL,10,Fthe Online Safety Act has provided us
OL,11,Fwith more opportunities to ensure that
OL,12,Fthose who use digital platforms feel
OL,13,Fsafe when doing so, and those who
OL,14,Fchoose to abuse these platforms are
OL,15,Fcaught and brought before the courts."
OL,17,FThe teenager has been remanded into
OL,18,Fcustody until sentencing on 22 May.
